race.comment: INSPIRED LEGEND (3) returned last start over 1400m here and didn't warm to the task until the race was done and dusted. Fitter for that run and is perfectly placed out to the mile for the first time. LET'S BE HONEST (5) lines up for only the third time. Has lacked early pace in both runs but finds the line with purpose, most recently getting within 1.4 lengths of the winner over 1500m here. No surprise to see him shine over this slightly longer journey. SERPICO (9) found 1200m too sharp at Warwick Farm last time out. Fitter for two runs back from a break and is looking for this trip now. BONDI BLOSSOM (2) missed the maiden win by inches over 1500m here recently. Very fit filly who is sure to attract plenty of interest.
